{
  "stem": "3085.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 24,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And, and so he felt that nothing could be done to him or to his family or Jews who were-- who felt so Hungarian and so-- so patriotic, if you like.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I mean, there were-- there were some covert discrimination, I suppose.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But nothing-- no, there was no overt anti-Semitism or-- until quite late.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, he, he went-- he, he, you know, he did very well in his business.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he had a lot of Christian clients.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I mean, it wasn't like in Germany, where, at some point, people were discouraged from buying-- you know, going to Jewish stores and deal with Jews.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "No, he had a lot of Christian clients and customers.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And no, he was-- he was doing all right.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I mean, we didn't have-- I mean, the fact that I-- we went to a, a Catholic school, I think, even as, as external students, or special students, attest to the fact that, you know, Jews were tolerated, if nothing else.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 25,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And there were no-- there was no overt discrimination until, until, until the German invasion.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, of course, that was in 1940-- March 19, 1944 when the Germans invaded-- essentially, invaded Hungary.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And, and they took over, more or less.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And not just them, but the faction of, of, of the Hungarian government, or the Hungarian parties, that were pro-Nazi took over.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And things changed very rapidly.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 26,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Within weeks, I think, we had to start wearing the yellow Star of David.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "It was the law.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, I, I think one day, it's just-- it was proclaimed as the law.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And, and I recall I was probably 10 years old or thereabouts-- was it-- yeah, it was 1944.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I was 10 or 11 years old.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
